{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/WishListGame.gif?t=1735989517\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/Game_Title_1.png?t=1735989517\" />Whispers of the Tarnished City immerses players in a captivating action-adventure experience while blending Puzzle-solving, Mystery, and Exploration elements. The game transports you to a sci-fi post-apocalyptic metropolis city, once so vibrant but now lies in ruins, engulfed by magic. Step into the shoes of the exiled son of the King of The Royal City, ousted from his rightful throne by a duplicitous stepbrother.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And your objective is clear:  Uncover the secrets and escape the Tarnished City before you are consumed within it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/Interior_1_LowRes.gif?t=1735989517\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/ExploreTitle.png?t=1735989517\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/Interior_6_LowRes.gif?t=1735989517\" />&quot;Whispers of the Tarnished City&quot; features diverse areas within the island's levels, each with its unique atmosphere and challenges. You navigate through post-apocalyptic industrial ruins and ascend crumbling structures as you uncover the island's secrets. From the eerie tranquillity of abandoned research facilities to the perilous heights of overgrown skyscrapers, every area tries to offer a different and unique experience. <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/Interior_5_LowRes.gif?t=1735989517\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A forgotten secret Lab ran hidden away from the world's prying eyes where the secrets of the current world's origins lie hidden. The mysteries concealed within its walls, encountering forgotten experiments and mysterious figures. Who's inside and who you will find...<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/Interior_3_LowRes.gif?t=1735989517\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/DefendCreactureTitle.png?t=1735989517\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/extras/Interior_7_LowRes.gif?t=1735989517\" />Prepare to encounter mysterious enemies lurking in the shadows of the game's world. These mysterious foes wield arcane powers and unleash unknown forces upon you when least expected.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you navigate the Tarnished City, stay vigilant against these cryptic adversaries... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The PC version of the game features (some of the things are still a work in progress): </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">High-resolution textures</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The highest-quality game models will be visible.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Higher amount of Visual Effects worldwide.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">More Physics based environments</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Indirect Shadows</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Foliage</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2976780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735989517","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/s